    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Attius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Voturia Exor<lb break="no" n="3"/>atus miles <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apo</abbr><ex>llinaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> XXXXIV <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>stipend</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> XXIIII <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Minicius et <lb n="8"/>Suc<expan><ex>c</ex><abbr>es</abbr><ex>s</ex><abbr>us</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> posierunt <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Über dem gerahmten Inschriftfeld Straßenszene: Ochsengespann mit Mann in paenula, Peitsche haltend; vor dem Gespann miles in peanula und tunica, hinter dem Wagen Hund. Datierung nach Grabmaltypologie. Nach Ubl aufgrund der bogenförmig geschürzten tunica flavisch. (B): Z. 3: Vorbeck: ann(orum).</p>
            </div>
